## Doctrine alignment

This proposal targets doctrine `{{.Doctrine}}`. The change is
operator-gated (Q10 C); the amendment NEVER auto-applies. The cooldown
window suppresses re-proposal of the same trigger pattern for the
doctrine's `proposal_cooldown_hours`.

